docs {
  # Atlas Indexing API

  This collection targets the Atlas `/indexing` module.

  Notes:
  - Tenant in path must match the JWT tenant claim, or the JWT must contain `tenants: ["*"]`.
  - `02-create-ingestion` stores returned `jobId` for later requests.
  - Stop route is included: `08-stop-ingestions` (`POST /indexing/tenants/{{tenantId}}/ingestions/stop`).
  - Cleanup route is included: `07-delete-all-ingestions` (`DELETE /indexing/tenants/{{tenantId}}/ingestions`).
}
